  <summary date="2018-05-29T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Liberty City Rising Act

This bill requires the Department of Housing and Urban Development to establish standards to ensure the safety and security of federally assisted housing in high-crime areas. Public housing agencies serving high-crime areas must establish anonymous hotlines for tenants to report suspicious activity and crimes in the community.</summary>
